Hi All,
I'm making a request to a customer API in Magento, but I'm receiving the response as a string instead of an array or object. How can I parse and process the response?
Here's my code:
```php

$url = "<https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/contacts?limit=100&amp;after=6560920356&amp;properties=HubSpot_owner_id>"; 
$token = $this-&gt;modelData-&gt;getAccessToken(); 
$headers = [ 'Content-Type: application/json', 'Authorization: Bearer ' . $token ]; 

$this-&gt;curl-&gt;write('GET', $url, $http_ver = '', $headers); 
$response = $this-&gt;curl-&gt;read(); ```
Any suggestions on how to handle this response?
